## Quantization Scheme
- **Primary**: 6-bit integer quantization (per-row) for most tensors
- **Embeddings**: 8-bit quantization for token embeddings (tok_emb.weight)
- **Compression**: zstandard (zstd) compression applied to serialized model
- **Control tensors**: Kept in FP16 (scales, gains, residual mixing weights)

## Key Features
- Mixed-precision quantization optimizes for compression while maintaining quality
- Stochastic Weight Averaging helps convergence stability
- GQA reduces KV cache memory requirements
- Muon optimizer provides efficient matrix updates
